('56677','19869','5','4 star hotel rural with restaurant '),
('56678','19870','5','This country estate was purchased in 1978 by its present owner and is located on a plot of 58,000 m². In 1984 it was expanded on a grand scale, creating 20 guest rooms including 6 large family rooms. In 2000, the country house was renovated extensively and equipped with a solar assisted oil-fired central heating and air conditioning.\r\nAll 20 guest rooms are located in single-storey houses with terraces, surrounded by beautifully landscaped gardens. They are decorated in Mallorcan style and feature heating, air conditioning, bathroom and telephone.\r\nThe main building houses the reception, the restaurant for 40 people, a conference room for up to 30 people, a kitchen with storage room and two guest toilets. Upstairs there is an apartment of 90 m² comprising of living room, office room, bedroom and bathroom.\r\nThe water supply realizes a private well with a flow rate that is sufficient for 500 beds.\r\nFurthermore, the property boasts a swimming pool of 13x13 m surrounded by sun terraces, a riding arena with horse stables, a 1,000 m² parking lot, landscaped gardens with mature trees, Mediterranean plants and more than 40 fruit trees.\r\nSeminars and conferences have successfully taken place here since many years. Both, business groups and holiday makers enjoy the special atmosphere and the rural setting of this hotel.'),
